%E1%BB%97-M%E1%BB%A5c/L%E1%BB%AF-t%C3%BAc/poem-kBdgVic3JnKgw1IGHv_v2g">Lữ túc - 旅宿</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-M%E1%BB%A5c/author-3vzgm_fq7JLuFBSuENsFJw">Đỗ Mục</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93ng-L%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-C%C3%A1t/Ng%C3%B4-Mai-Th%C3%B4n-t%E1%BB%AB-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-b%C3%ADch/poem-ygcr3qgUFCOlwgvaqnjPsQ">Ngô Mai Thôn từ đề bích - 吳梅村祠題壁</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93ng-L%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-C%C3%A1t/author-rT4JE0Ax7ttoqnPYUvKzPg">Hồng Lượng Cát</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-%E1%BB%A8c/Th%C6%B0-ho%C3%A0i-ph%E1%BB%A5ng-tr%C3%ACnh-C%C3%BAc-%C4%90%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-ch%E1%BB%A7-nh%C3%A2n/poem-Qx0tgzKdHgbmPhUBW2JlQg">Thư hoài phụng trình Cúc Đường chủ nhân - 書懷奉呈菊堂主人</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-%E1%BB%A8c/author-KitWPFSrhqgQGR4JMcSBew">Nguyễn Ức</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Duy/T%E1%BB%91ng-B%C3%AD-th%C6%B0-Tri%E1%BB%81u-Gi%C3%A1m-ho%C3%A0n-Nh%E1%BA%ADt-B%E1%BA%A3n/poem-sFOIFUbLJa3x5wZMjutrJA">Tống Bí thư Triều Giám hoàn Nhật Bản - 送祕書晁監還日本並序</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Duy/author-9f1Hth0gmM_PXzGNXg5Fog">Vương Duy</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
